snippet.title: Dooria Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Second trailer for Dooria, showing a bit more of the game.

Game is available on Steam and itch.io and is half price until the end of September.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1343990/Dooria/
https://paperatom.itch.io/dooria

For more information, visit https://dooriagame.com/
